With regard to PRP participation, the Department's regulations require that trustee officials provide PRPs with
a Notice of Intent to Perform an Assessment before beginning an assessment and invite the participation of the PRPs.
See 43 CFR 11.32(a)(2), as amended by 59 FR 14282. Trustee officials are also required to make the Assessment Plan available
